library(ggplot2)
library(MASS)    # dplyr    .
data("Cars93")   # MASS  Cars93  .

Basic_Plot <- ggplot(Cars93, aes(x=Price, y=Horsepower)) + # x:  , y: 
                geom_point(aes(colour=DriveTrain))  # jitter plot . :
